@startuml
'title and flow for product discovery and shipping quote happy path.
title 01 - Busca de Produto e Cotação de Frete - Fluxo Feliz

autonumber
actor Buyer as Comprador
participant "Marketplace Web" as FE
participant "Marketplace BFF" as BFF
participant "Product Search Service" as Search
participant "Product Catalog Service" as Catalog
participant "Shipping Promise Service" as Promise
participant "Inventory Service" as Inventory
participant "Fulfillment Center Service" as FC
participant "Routing Service" as Routing
participant "Carrier Service" as Carrier
participant "Shipping Pricing Service" as Pricing

Comprador -> FE: Digita termo de busca
FE -> BFF: GET /api/web/v1/products/search?query=iphone&page=1&pageSize=20
BFF -> Search: GET /v1/products/search?query=iphone&page=1&pageSize=20
Search --> BFF: ProductSearchResponse
BFF --> FE: Product cards paginados
FE --> Comprador: Lista produtos ofertados

Comprador -> FE: Seleciona produto e informa CEP
FE -> BFF: GET /api/web/v1/products/{skuId}/page?quantity=1&zipCode={cep}
BFF -> Catalog: GET /products/{skuId}
Catalog --> BFF: ProductResponse

BFF -> Promise: POST /shipping-promises/
activate Promise
Promise -> Catalog: POST /products/physical-info/batch
Catalog --> Promise: ProductPhysicalInfoResponse[]
Promise -> Inventory: POST /inventory/availability/batch
Inventory --> Promise: InventoryAvailabilityResponse[]
Promise -> FC: POST /fulfillment-centers/candidates/search
FC --> Promise: FulfillmentCandidateResponse[]
Promise -> Routing: POST /routes/search
Routing --> Promise: RouteSearchResponse
Promise -> Carrier: POST /carrier-availability/search
Carrier --> Promise: CarrierAvailabilitySearchResponse
Promise -> Pricing: POST /shipping-prices/quotes/batch
Pricing --> Promise: BatchShippingPriceResponse
Promise --> BFF: ShippingPromiseResponse available=true
deactivate Promise

BFF --> FE: ProductPageResponse com product + shipping
FE --> Comprador: Exibe preço, prazo, carrier e custo

@enduml
